{"tid":1432223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【福建自治】復興地方分權運動","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:41:59.000Z","uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"849c1ca5ab216422d9a410dc0e9c1c6752efefc3","tid":1432223,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"徒以主權為萬能、為惟一、為神聖不可侵犯，且為國家所獨有，則行使此主權者，無論如何制限其權力，流弊所至，必為專制，專制之極，必肇革命。<br />\n<br />\n蓋人民利害情感及職業趣味，各有不同，國家為政治最高團體，其所以圖謀增進人民之福祉者，在於職務之分配得宜，不在於大權之獨攬。<br />\n<br />\n領導中國改革開放發展的鄧小平，亦是地方分權運動的推手，可惜後繼無人，回頭走向集權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n福建省憲法（1926）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%9C%81%E6%86%B2%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2586%25B2%25E6%25B3%2595&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=10b5f31f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%9C%81%E6%86%B2%E6%B3%95</a>"}]}